snippet.title: Operation Blackout | Season 6 Gameplay Trailer - Arena Breakout
snippet.description:
Get ready for the adrenaline-pumping action of Arena Breakout Season 6! Fasten your seatbelts! Overcome the odds! Apart from the thrilling Story Missions, here come even more new features:
1. NEW HIGH-TIER LOOT
2. NEW GUNS
3. NEW VEHICLE SKINS
4. NORTHRIDGE ROYALE
5. THE FOBBIDEN ZONE
